Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五閃神弓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(355,323)\fs18}Necronomicon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧  死靈之書
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Gungnir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恆之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上吧  伊莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所供給  即為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之所求  是為殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,323)\fs18}Marduk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對龍兵器  馬爾杜克  主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Bavel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖天之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴西利斯克即將到達距離六公里的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾列拉同學  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量源源不斷地湧入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們給它來個貫穿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  伊莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴西利斯克已到達距離六公里的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9  8  7
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6  5
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緹婭  我要用這一擊來結束你的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4  3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴  巴西利斯克從第三隻眼發起了反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次站在大家面前的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地對沒能適應的我搭話的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠同學  就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.47,0:23:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學  雖然只是一段短暫的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是非常感謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  銃皇無盡的法夫納
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天而降的米斯特汀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.10,0:24:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠同學  我們肯定仍會在某個地方再次相見吧
